item.title: Project 1: Exploratory Data Analysis
item.description: Desiree Kibbee EID: dlk897 Data Wrangling For this project I have created two datasets. The first dataset is called txstatistics, from the CDC website I chose 50 random texas cities and documented their 2019 population (population variable), the percent of persons with a bachelors degree or higher (percent_bach variable), and the average household income for 2019 (avg_income variable). The second dataset is called txhomevalues; from Zillow.
